<h2>Margaret Lake to Beaufort Sea </h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>III-IV (for normal flows) </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-2'>
<th>Length</th>
<td>99 Miles </td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class='river-photo'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>Firth River</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzq94gqk3rokhknPhotoDetailView67' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='river-photo'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/8546/size/big/">
<img class='river-photo' src="/photos/archive/medium/8546.jpg">
